{"word":"Joel","slug":"joel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Joel</b> <a href=\"#/H3100\">H3100</a> <br/> 1. Son of Samuel<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=2'>1Sa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=33'>1Ch 6:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=17'>1Ch 15:17</a> <br/> - Called Vashni<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=28'>1Ch 6:28</a> <br/> 2. A Simeonite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=35'>1Ch 4:35</a><br/> 3. A Reubenite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=4'>1Ch 5:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Ch 5:8</a><br/> 4. A Gadite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=12'>1Ch 5:12</a><br/> 5. A Kohathite Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=36'>1Ch 6:36</a><br/> 6. Descendant of Issachar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=3'>1Ch 7:3</a><br/> 7. One of David's valiant men<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=38'>1Ch 11:38</a> <br/> - Called &#187;Igal, son of Nathan&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=36'>2Sa 23:36</a> <br/> 8. Name of two Gershonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Ch 15:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=11'>1Ch 15:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=8'>1Ch 23:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=22'>1Ch 26:22</a><br/> 9. Prince of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=20'>1Ch 27:20</a><br/> 10. A Kohathite who assisted in the cleansing of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=12'>2Ch 29:12</a><br/> 11. One of Nebo's family<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=43'>Ezr 10:43</a><br/> 12. Son of Zichri<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=9'>Neh 11:9</a><br/> 13. One of the twelve minor prophets, probably lived in the days of Uzziah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1&verse=1'>Joe 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=16'>Act 2:16</a> <br/> - Declares the terribleness of God's judgments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1'>Joe 1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=11'>Joe 2:11</a> <br/> - Exhorts to repentance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=32'>Joe 2:32</a> <br/> - Denounces judgments against the enemies of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=17'>Joe 3:17</a> <br/> - Sets forth the blessings of the church<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=21'>Joe 3:21</a> "}]}